Class MoodRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.moodroid.repository.BaseRepository
      • ca.ualberta.moodroid.repository.MoodRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RepositoryInterface

    @Singleton
public class MoodRepository
extends BaseRepository
    This repository stores all of our static moods, Happy, Angry, Sad, Annoyed, Sick, and Scared, along with their unique data. Users use these mood concepts to make mood event which go in that repository.
